Nothing special here:

this map was to practice with every technique in hammer and some failed

note:
please PM me if their are any textures missing

also their a BAK.Bsp file in there idk what it is but i left it with the other one

how its played:
both teams start on a platform at the very top of the map with no weapons, the idea is that both teams jump of through the death sphere through the pipers to collect their knife, both teams can teleport back to the top to kill any AFKs,and knife. if you fall of the platforms you'll get teleported into the death sphere where you will....well die.
